> May 19 - Tobacco ban came into effect in public and closed areas. 
> July 27 - An explosion occurred in Istanbul's Gungoren district: 17 dead, 154 injured. (see the 2008 Gungoren attack)
> July 30 - The Constitutional Court rejected the request for closure on the Justice and Development Party because the required 7 votes were not obtained.
 The trial started 4.5 months ago. 
> October 3 - PKK attacked Semdinli Aktutun Gendarmerie Station in Semdinli district of Hakkari with heavy weapons.
